cent\">+$15<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-compare-row\" style=\"grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;min-width:600px\"><div>TIFF files<\/div><div>+$1<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">Free<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">Free<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">Free<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-compare-row\" style=\"grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;min-width:600px\"><div>Sleeving &amp; negative return<\/div><div>+$2<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">Free<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">Free<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">Free<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-compare-row\" style=\"grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;min-width:600px\"><div>Monthly credits<\/div><div>&mdash;<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">1 roll free<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">3 rolls free<\/div><div class=\"mem-compare-accent\">7 rolls free ($126 value)<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><!-- \/mem-compare-desktop -->\n\n<!-- MOBILE COMPARISON TABS -->\n<div class=\"mem-compare-mobile\">\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-btns\">\n<button class=\"mem-ctab-btn\" onclick=\"showCtab('casual')\">Casual<\/button>\n<button class=\"mem-ctab-btn active\" onclick=\"showCtab('enth')\">Enthusiast<\/button>\n<button class=\"mem-ctab-btn\" onclick=\"showCtab('serious')\" style=\"color:var(--accent)\">Serious<\/button>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"ctab-casual\" class=\"mem-ctab-panel\">\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Develop &amp; scan<\/div><div>$16 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members $18)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Medium scan<\/div><div>Included<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>High 4K scan<\/div><div>+$6 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$12)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Pro scan<\/div><div>+$15 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$18)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>TIFF files<\/div><div>Free <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$1)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Sleeving<\/div><div>Free <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$2)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Monthly credits<\/div><div>1 roll free<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"ctab-enth\" class=\"mem-ctab-panel active\">\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Develop &amp; scan<\/div><div>$16 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members $18)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Medium scan<\/div><div>Included<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>High 4K scan<\/div><div>+$6 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$12)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Pro scan<\/div><div>+$15 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$18)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>TIFF files<\/div><div>Free <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$1)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Sleeving<\/div><div>Free <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$2)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Monthly credits<\/div><div>3 rolls free<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"ctab-serious\" class=\"mem-ctab-panel\">\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Develop &amp; scan<\/div><div>$16 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members $18)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Medium scan<\/div><div>Included<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>High 4K scan<\/div><div>+$4 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$12)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Pro scan<\/div><div>+$15 <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$18)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>TIFF files<\/div><div>Free <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$1)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Sleeving<\/div><div>Free <span style=\"color:var(--muted);font-weight:400\">(non members +$2)<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-ctab-row\"><div>Monthly credits<\/div><div>7 rolls free ($126 value)<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><!-- \/mem-compare-mobile -->\n\n<hr class=\"mem-divider\">\n\n<!-- CALCULATOR -->\n<p class=\"mem-label\" id=\"savings-calculator\">Savings calculator<\/p>\n<div class=\"mem-calc\">\n<div class=\"mem-calc-head\">\n<div class=\"mem-calc-title\">How much would you save?<\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-calc-sub\">Tell us how you shoot and we&rsquo;ll show you your monthly cost at each tier.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-calc-body\">\n<div class=\"mem-calc-row\">\n<div class=\"mem-calc-field\">\n<label>Rolls per month<\/label>\n<input type=\"number\" id=\"calc-rolls\" min=\"1\" max=\"50\" value=\"4\" oninput=\"calcSavings()\">\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-calc-field\">\n<label>Scan quality<\/label>\n<select id=\"calc-scan\" onchange=\"calcSavings()\">\n<option value=\"0\">Medium (included)<\/option>\n<option value=\"12\" data-member=\"6\">High 4K (+$12 \/ +$6 member)<\/option>\n<option value=\"18\" data-member=\"15\">Pro (+$18 \/ +$15 member)<\/option>\n<\/select>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p style=\"font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px;\">Add-ons<\/p>\n<div class=\"mem-calc-addons\">\n<div class=\"mem-calc-addon\" id=\"addon-tiff\" onclick=\"toggleAddon('tiff')\">TIFF +$1 \/ Free<\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-calc-addon on\" id=\"addon-sleeves\" onclick=\"toggleAddon('sleeves')\">Sleeving +$2 \/ Free<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mem-calc-results\" id=\"calc-results\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"mem-credit-note\">\n<strong>How credits work:<\/strong> Each membership comes with monthly Dev+Scan credits deposited automatically. Each credit covers <strong>$18 off your developing order<\/strong>. Casual Shooters get 1 credit\/mo, Enthusiasts get 3. Credits roll over up to 50 and never expire while your membership is active.\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div><!-- \/mem-section -->\n<\/div><!-- \/bfc-mem -->\n\n<script>\n(function(){\nvar billing='monthly';\n\/\/ Mobile swipe: clone plan cards into swipe track\n(function(){\n  if(window.innerWidth > 768) return;\n  var track = document.getElementById('swipe-track');\n  if(!track) return;\n  \/\/ Hide desktop label + lower plans on mobile\n  var dl = document.getElementById('desktop-plans-label');\n  var dp = document.getElementById('desktop-plans-lower');\n  if(dl) dl.style.display='none';\n  if(dp) dp.style.display='none';\n  \/\/ Grab cards: enthusiast from hero-card, casual+serious from lower\n  var heroCard = document.querySelector('.mem-hero-card .mem-plan');\n  var lowerCards = document.querySelectorAll('.mem-plans-lower .mem-plan');\n  \/\/ Order for mobile swipe: Casual, Enthusiast (hero), Serious\n  var casualCard = lowerCards[0]; \/\/ Casual is first in lower\n  var seriousCard = lowerCards[1]; \/\/ Serious is second in lower\n  var cards = [];\n  if(casualCard) cards.push(casualCard);\n  if(heroCard) cards.push(heroCard);\n  if(seriousCard) cards.push(seriousCard);\n  cards.forEach(function(card){\n    var wrap = document.createElement('div');\n    wrap.className = 'mem-swipe-card';\n    var clone = card.cloneNode(true);\n    clone.style.cssText = '';\n    wrap.appendChild(clone);\n    track.appendChild(wrap);\n  });\n  \/\/ Auto-scroll to Enthusiast (middle card) after layout\n  setTimeout(function(){\n    var middle = track.querySelector('.mem-swipe-card:nth-child(2)');\n    if(middle) track.scrollLeft = middle.offsetLeft - 20;\n  }, 100);\n})();\n\nwindow.showCtab=function(tab){\n  ['casual','enth','serious'].forEach(function(t){\n    document.getElementById('ctab-'+t).classList.toggle('active',t===tab);\n    document.querySelectorAll('.mem-ctab-btn').forEach(function(btn,i){\n      btn.classList.toggle('active',['casual','enth','serious'][i]===tab);\n    });\n  });\n};\nvar addons={tiff:false,sleeves:true};\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function(){calcSavings();});\n\nwindow.setBilling=function(b){\nbilling=b;\ndocument.getElementById('btn-monthly').classList.toggle('active',b==='monthly');\ndocument.getElementById('btn-yearly').classList.toggle('active',b==='yearly');\nvar isY=b==='yearly';\n['casual-price','enth-price','serious-price'].forEach(function(id){\n  var vals={'casual-price':isY?'$17.10<span>\/mo<\/span>':'$18<span>\/mo<\/span>','enth-price':isY?'$42.75<span>\/mo<\/span>':'$45<span>\/mo<\/span>','serious-price':isY?'$95<span>\/mo<\/span>':'$100<span>\/mo<\/span>'};\n  document.querySelectorAll('[id=\"'+id+'\"]').forEach(function(el){el.innerHTML=vals[id];});\n});\n['casual-yearly','enth-yearly','serious-yearly'].forEach(function(id){\n  var vals={'casual-yearly':isY?'<strong>$205.20<\/strong> billed annually':'&nbsp;','enth-yearly':isY?'<strong>$513.00<\/strong> billed annually':'&nbsp;','serious-yearly':isY?'<strong>$1,140<\/strong> billed annually':'&nbsp;'};\n  document.querySelectorAll('[id=\"'+id+'\"]').forEach(function(el){el.innerHTML=vals[id];});\n});\n['casual-monthly-btn','enth-monthly-btn','serious-monthly-btn'].forEach(function(id){document.querySelectorAll('[id=\"'+id+'\"]').forEach(function(el){el.style.display=isY?'none':'block';});});\n\/\/ Update credit values monthly vs yearly (use querySelectorAll to handle cloned mobile cards)\nfunction setAll(id,val){document.querySelectorAll('[id=\"'+id+'\"]').forEach(function(el){el.innerHTML=val;});}\nsetAll('casual-credit-text',isY?'12 free Dev+Scan credits\/yr':'1 free Dev+Scan credit\/mo');\nsetAll('casual-credit-val',isY?'$216 value':'$18 value');\nsetAll('enth-credit-text',isY?'36 free Dev+Scan credits\/yr':'3 free Dev+Scan credits\/mo');\nsetAll('enth-credit-val',isY?'$648 value':'$54 value');\nsetAll('serious-credit-text',isY?'84 free Dev+Scan credits\/yr':'7 free Dev+Scan credits\/mo');\nsetAll('serious-credit-val',isY?'$1,512 value':'$126 value');\n['casual-yearly-btn','enth-yearly-btn','serious-yearly-btn'].forEach(function(id){document.querySelectorAll('[id=\"'+id+'\"]').forEach(function(el){el.style.display=isY?'block':'none';});});\ncalcSavings();\n};\n\nwindow.toggleAddon=function(k){\naddons[k]=!addons[k];\ndocument.getElementById('addon-'+k).classList.toggle('on',addons[k]);\ncalcSavings();\n};\n\nfunction fmt(c){return '$'+c.toFixed(2);}\n\nwindow.calcSavings=function(){\nvar rolls=Math.max(1,parseInt(document.getElementById('calc-rolls').value)||4);\nvar scanEl=document.getElementById('calc-scan');\nvar scanGuest=parseFloat(scanEl.value)||0;\nvar scanMember=parseFloat(scanEl.options[scanEl.selectedIndex].dataset.member||0);\nvar tiffGuest=addons.tiff?1:0;\nvar sleeveGuest=addons.sleeves?2:0;\nvar sleeveMember=0;\n\n\/\/ All values in dollars\nvar guestPerRoll=18+scanGuest+tiffGuest+sleeveGuest;\nvar memberPerRoll=16+scanMember+sleeveMember; \/\/ tiff free, sleeves $0.50 for members\n\nvar guestTotal=guestPerRoll*rolls;\n\nvar casualFee=billing==='yearly'?17.10:18;\nvar enthFee=billing==='yearly'?42.75:45;\n\nvar casualCreditVal=Math.min(1,rolls)*18;\nvar casualTotal=casualFee+(memberPerRoll*rolls)-casualCreditVal;\n\nvar enthCreditVal=Math.min(3,rolls)*18;\nvar enthTotal=enthFee+(memberPerRoll*rolls)-enthCreditVal;\n\nvar casualSave=guestTotal-casualTotal;\nvar enthSave=guestTotal-enthTotal;\n\n\/\/ Serious Shooter: $100\/mo, 7 credits, 4K=$4\nvar seriousFee=billing==='yearly'?95:100;\nvar seriousPerRoll=16+(scanMember===6?4:scanMember)+sleeveMember;\nvar seriousCreditVal=Math.min(7,rolls)*18;\nvar seriousTotal=seriousFee+(seriousPerRoll*rolls)-seriousCreditVal;\nvar seriousSave=guestTotal-seriousTotal;\n\nvar res=document.getElementById('calc-results');\nvar saves=[{k:'guest',v:0},{k:'casual',v:casualSave},{k:'enth',v:enthSave},{k:'serious',v:seriousSave}];\nsaves.sort(function(a,b){return b.v-a.v;});\nvar best=saves[0].v>0?saves[0].k:'guest';\n\nres.innerHTML=\n'<div class=\"mem-calc-result'+(best==='guest'?' highlight':'')+'\">'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-name\">Non Member<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-total\">'+fmt(guestTotal)+'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-mo\">per month<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-saving\" style=\"color:var(--muted)\">No membership<\/div>'+\n'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-calc-result'+(best==='casual'?' highlight':'')+'\">'+\n(best==='casual'?'<div class=\"mem-result-tag\">Best for you<\/div>':'')+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-name\">Casual Shooter<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-total\">'+fmt(casualTotal)+'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-mo\">per month incl. membership<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-saving\">'+(casualSave>0?'Save '+fmt(casualSave)+' vs non member':'')+'<\/div>'+\n'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-calc-result'+(best==='enth'?' highlight':'')+'\">'+\n(best==='enth'?'<div class=\"mem-result-tag\">Best for you<\/div>':'')+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-name\">Enthusiast<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-total\">'+fmt(enthTotal)+'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-mo\">per month incl. membership<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-saving\">'+(enthSave>0?'Save '+fmt(enthSave)+' vs non member':'')+'<\/div>'+\n'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-calc-result'+(best==='serious'?' best':'')+'\">'+\n(best==='serious'?'<div class=\"mem-result-tag\">Best for you<\/div>':'')+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-name\">Serious Shooter<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-total\">'+fmt(seriousTotal)+'<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-mo\">per month incl. membership<\/div>'+\n'<div class=\"mem-result-saving\">'+(seriousSave>0?'Save '+fmt(seriousSave)+' vs non member':'')+'<\/div>'+\n'<\/div>';\n};\n\ncalcSavings();\n})();\n<\/script>","section_width":"max-w-fluid","color_scheme":"","spacing_top":"0","spacing_bottom":"0"}}},"order":["main","membership"]}